tures<br>? New spells and enemies<br>? New region of Meliora to explore<br>? New Game+, Hardcore Mode and Sandbox Arena Mode <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1103860\/extras\/Image_1.png?t=1727354110\" \/>","short_description":"Face the end of the world in the sequel to The Wizards. The critically acclaimed VR spellcaster returns with a gesture-based system, challenging enemies, grand adventure, and the ever-witty narrator.","supported_languages":"英语<strong>*<\/strong>, 法语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 简体中文, 意大利语, 日语, 韩语<br><strong>*<\/strong>具有完全音频支持的语言","reviews":"“The best spell-casting VR game ever made”<br>80\/100 – Gaming Trend<br><br>“By the end, you’ll feel like an earth-shattering powerhouse of arcane fury.”<br>4\/5 – UploadVR<br><br>“Once all the spells are unlocked the magic system showcases why VR is a natural fit this style of videogame”<br>4\/5 – VRFocus<br>","header_image":"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1103860\/header.jpg?t=1727354110","capsule_image":"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1103860\/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1727354110","capsule_imagev5":"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1103860\/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1727354110","website":"http:\/\/darktimesgame.com\/","pc_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>最低配置:<\/strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>需要 64 位处理器和操作系统<br><\/li><li><strong>操作系统:<\/strong> Windows 10<br><\/li><li><strong>处理器:<\/strong> Intel i7-4790 \/ AMD Ryzen 5 1600 or greater (only Oculus Rift, for Vive see Recomended spec)<br><\/li><li><strong>内存:<\/strong> 8 GB RAM<br><\/li><li><strong>显卡:<\/strong> NVIDIA GTX 2060 or greater (only Oculus Rift, for Vive see Recomended spec)<br><\/li><li><strong>存储空间:<\/strong> 需要 20 GB 可用空间<br><\/li><li><strong>支持 VR:<\/strong> SteamVR or Oculus PC<br><\/li><li><strong>附注事项:<\/strong> Supported Devices: Valve Index, HTC Vive, Oc